            Be bold where the upside is huge and the downside small. Day-to-day, move slow and steady.  
            It beats burnout culture every time for me.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md text-center">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-accent mb-3">Random Weakness</h3>
